Description: 

Welcome to the infinite vacation, where changing your life is alway just a click way! Mark lives in a world where alternate realities are up for sale, and buying and trading your way through unlimited variations of yourself is as commonplace as checking your email or updating your status. But when other "hims" start dying suddenly and he meets a mysterious girl who wants nothing to do with "life-changing," he'll learn the truth about the universe he stumbles through, and what happens when your vacation turns on you. 

From the writer of the hit series Morning Glories and the artist of Olympus! An epic high concept sci-fi love story perfect for fans of Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind, (500) Days of Summer,and Inception.
